    <p>
        Welcome! We are an enthusiastic group of students who hope to eliminate homophobia and transphobia at St. Clair College through education and awareness. We want to provide support and a place to be yourself so we host a number of social events as well where you can meet new people and come to hang out. We are a fairly new club but we are growing fast. Contact us to get involved &ndash; we are always looking for new members!
    </p>
