            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>
                    The St. Clair College Gay-Straight Alliance is a club which was sanctioned under SRC for the first time in September, 2014. The GSA is proud to be the first non-program based club to exist as a
                    ratified SRC club in the history of St. Clair College and caused a revision to be made in the legislation for club ratification. This now allows all interest-based clubs to be recognized under SRC
                    (pending appropriate documentation required by all clubs) and receive all advantages of a program-based club except for the funding.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Since the initial ratification, the GSA has been an extremely active club, hosting monthly events and attending even more events in the community to lend our support and resources. Meetings fluctuate
                    days and times to accommodate a variety of class schedules, but occur nearly every week.
                </p>
